<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>-<span class="c5"> صيام التطوع وأحكامه:</span> <span class="c2">«زاد المعاد»</span> ٢/ ٨٠<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
